{"tid":1160681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"意甲官方宣佈，C朗當選今季意甲MVP","createTime":"2019-05-18T15:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T10:13:29.000Z","uid":173952,"like":18,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"bc14f7d2fcf7a8272dbbaf17e4070dd05654fc97","tid":1160681,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"5月18日訊 意甲聯盟官方宣布，C羅當選本賽季意甲MVP，他在33場比賽里打進22球助攻11次。<br />\n 意甲評選使用Opta和Netco的數據，參考球員在意甲、意大利杯和意大利超級杯中的表現，國米門將漢達諾維奇被評為最佳門將，那不勒斯後衛庫利巴利被評為最佳後衛 ，拉齊奧中場米林科維奇被評為最佳中場，桑普多利亞老將誇利亞雷拉以26球當選最佳前鋒，羅馬中場扎尼奧洛被評為最佳年輕球員。"},{"pid":"fd23a744496131709583329b6ff64853fced881e","tid":1160681,"uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"正式集齊 英超西甲意甲Mvp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2552b15d131fe6d11458a980f11a698da07bae","tid":1160681,"uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"過唔過2頁?"},{"pid":"91dc4d3fbd4f97d572502d5492ccfc8ff5bf1885","tid":1160681,"uid":247610,"like":95,"dislike":25,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"咁嘅表現都mvp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果1然真係靠marketing"},{"pid":"6920b5d54db4f1aaa9bda6940efc18341fc799a1","tid":1160681,"uid":200801,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"唔計啦 今年淨係計神射手"},{"pid":"00a40473fde6b171d0ffd0d195f85db84f1bfd3b","tid":1160681,"uid":216477,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43475adaf1fe4d731b5cff8d6f5be17e916af0ce","tid":1160681,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"whoelse"},{"pid":"b454313d8e14dae1748867d1c3fd4a579e1a4ecc","tid":1160681,"uid":173952,"like":27,"dislike":20,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"91dc4d3fbd4f97d572502d5492ccfc8ff5bf1885","tid":1160681,"uid":247610,"like":9